# PurePets SwiftUI Root Refactor — Comprehensive Build Readiness & Risk Audit Report

This report presents a thorough build-readiness audit, deployment target evaluation, runtime crash risk assessment, and Xcode integration checklist for the generated `PurePetsSwiftUIRefactor/Root/` architecture.

---

## 1. Runtime-Crash Risk Report

| Risk ID | Feature / Component | Analyzed Code Pattern | Risk Assessment & Mitigation Status |
| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **RCR-01** | Avatar Dynamic Invocation | `PPModernAvatarRenderer` method reflection | **MITIGATED**. Replaced `unsafeBitCast` with type-safe `perform(_:with:with:)` message dispatching and default placeholder fallback renderer. Zero `unsafeBitCast` pointer operations. |
| **RCR-02** | Lottie Framework Linkage | `LOTAnimationView` instantiation | **MITIGATED**. Safely checks `NSClassFromString(@"LOTAnimationView")` and `NSSelectorFromString(@"animationNamed:")` with standard SF Symbol vector fallback. No runtime exception risk if Lottie pod is missing. |
| **RCR-03** | Navigation Delegate Proxy | `UINavigationControllerDelegate` forwarding | **MITIGATED**. `PPRootNavigationDelegateProxy` implements `responds(to:)` and `forwardingTarget(for:)` safely with `Selector?` optionality. Prevents delegate overrides or unhandled selector crashes. |
| **RCR-04** | Cart Auto-Collapse Timer | `PPRootStore` 6.0s timer management | **MITIGATED**. Main-thread scheduled timer with weak self-capturing closures and explicit cancellation on `stop()` / `deinit`. Prevents retain cycles or post-dealloc callback execution. |
| **RCR-05** | Hit-Test Pass-Through | `PPRootPassthroughHostingController` | **MITIGATED**. Overrides `hitTest(_:with:)` to return `nil` for touches outside interactive elements (`PPRootDock`, `PPRootNovaButton`, `PPCartFloatingBarView`), permitting full gesture pass-through to underlying UIKit views. |

