## 6. Manual Xcode Integration Sequence

1. Open `Pure Pets.xcworkspace` in Xcode.
2. Drag `PurePetsSwiftUIRefactor/Root/` folder into Xcode project navigator under `Pure Pets/MainApp/ModrenAppVC/`.
3. Select **"Copy items if needed"** = unchecked (keep reference) and **Target Membership** = `Pure Pets`.
4. Add `PPRootParityTests.swift` to `Pure PetsTests` target.
5. Verify build setting `SWIFT_VERSION` = 5.0+.
6. Build project (Cmd+B) on a connected physical device.

